SEARCH
Package org.efs.timer.config

Class EfsScheduledExecutorConfig

java.lang.Object
org.efs.timer.config.EfsScheduledExecutorConfig
public final class EfsScheduledExecutorConfig extends Object
EfsScheduledExecutor configuration definition. Contains all properties required to build an EfsScheduledExecutor. This class is defined as a typesafe configuration bean.

Example EfsScheduledExecutorConfig File Entry

For further explanation on what these properties mean and valid settings, see property set method (e.g. setSpinLimit(long). 
executorName = "AlgoTimer"
threadType = SPINPARK
priority = 10
spinLimit = 250000000
parkTime = 500 nanos
Author:
Charles W. Rapp
